4. AI-Powered Visual Creation & Personalization
AI has transformed how visuals are created and personalized in 2026.
What AI Is Doing
•	Auto-generating design layouts
•	Creating motion graphics
•	Personalizing visuals based on user behavior
Real-Time Example
Canva AI suggests layouts, animations, and brand-consistent visuals.
Netflix personalizes thumbnails based on viewing behavior — a powerful visual marketing tactic.
