5. Visual Storytelling & Scrollytelling
Visual storytelling blends text, visuals, and motion into a narrative experience.
Why It Works
•	Keeps users engaged longera
•	Guides attention naturally
•	Improves content memorability
Real-Time Example
The New York Times uses scrollytelling in long-form stories combining images, animations, and data visuals.
